# PayKit

Payment provider integration toolkit for Python web frameworks.

## Installation

```bash
pip install paykit
```

## Usage

```bash
# Initialize configuration
paykit init

# Set framework
paykit set django

# Add payment provider
paykit add payme
```

## Supported Frameworks
- Django
- Flask

## Supported Providers
- Payme
- Click
- Stripe
